        <p>Commercial construction bidding is a different animal than residential. You're managing invitations to bid from multiple GCs, coordinating subcontractor coverage, leveling bids across dozens of line items, and operating on tight submission deadlines. The right software keeps you organized. The wrong software costs you bids.</p>

        <p>This guide focuses specifically on commercial bidding tools — bid management, subcontractor solicitation, and bid leveling — not general project management platforms.</p>

